<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id77230044-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s266"><num value="266">§ 266.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations for acquisition of additional lands</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">For the acquisition of lands authorized in <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s267">section 267 of this title</ref>, there are authorized to be appropriated such sums as may be necessary, but not more than $427,500.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id77230045-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/93/477/tI/s101/3">Pub. L. 93–477, title I, § 101(3)</ref>, <date date="1974-10-26">Oct. 26, 1974</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/88/1445">88 Stat. 1445</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id77230046-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id77230047-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="id77230048-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section was not enacted as part of <ref href="/us/act/1940-06-11/ch304">act June 11, 1940, ch. 304</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/54/262">54 Stat. 262</ref>, which comprises this subchapter.</p>
</note>
</notes>
